What is in the file: two sheets. One for mentions extracted from the event coreference sets in ECB/CEO. The second sheet covers mentions coming from the Semeval corpus vocabulary. All mentions, if not already covered by ECB/CEO, are listed here and are annotated.\
\
For ECB/CEO, 650 unique mentions were annotated with a total frequency of 3982.\
For Semeval, an additional 132 unique mentions were annotated. (No frequency numbers)\
